* An option to select if stdout and/or stderr are to be displayed.
* An option to show stderr output in red.
* An option to kill the underlying process if it goes idle (i.e., no
  output received for a certain period of time).
* An option to bounce in the dock on successful completion.
* An option to log the output to a file.
* An option to "nice" the process when it is run.

* An option to only display the output window when output appears.
